---
// ScienceDash is the shared substrate, not an agent runtime. Many Claude
// sessions read and write one project state through MCP.
---

<figure class="sub">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 720 408" role="img"
    aria-label="A central ScienceDash MCP substrate holding projects, hypotheses, runs, decisions and papers, read and written by three kinds of Claude session: dashboard buttons, a local terminal, and remote workhorses.">
    <defs>
      <marker id="sub-a" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8.5" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto">
        <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="var(--sl-color-gray-2)" />
      </marker>
    </defs>

    <!-- read/write connectors (drawn first, under the nodes) -->
    <line x1="360" y1="80" x2="360" y2="164" stroke="var(--sl-color-gray-3)" stroke-width="1.4" marker-start="url(#sub-a)" marker-end="url(#sub-a)" />
    <line x1="206" y1="330" x2="288" y2="262" stroke="var(--sl-color-gray-3)" stroke-width="1.4" marker-start="url(#sub-a)" marker-end="url(#sub-a)" />
    <line x1="520" y1="330" x2="436" y2="262" stroke="var(--sl-color-gray-3)" stroke-width="1.4" marker-start="url(#sub-a)" marker-end="url(#sub-a)" />

    <!-- centre: the substrate -->
    <rect x="222" y="166" width="276" height="92" rx="12" fill="var(--sl-color-bg)" stroke="var(--sl-color-accent)" stroke-width="1.6" />
    <text x="360" y="196" class="ctitle" text-anchor="middle">ScienceDash · shared MCP substrate</text>
    <text x="360" y="220" class="csub" text-anchor="middle">projects · hypotheses · runs</text>
    <text x="360" y="238" class="csub" text-anchor="middle">decisions · papers · notes</text>

    <!-- satellites -->
    <g>
      <rect x="283" y="36" width="154" height="44" rx="9" fill="var(--sl-color-bg)" stroke="var(--sl-color-hairline)" stroke-width="1.2" />
      <text x="360" y="63" class="sat" text-anchor="middle">Dashboard buttons</text>
    </g>
    <g>
      <rect x="62" y="330" width="170" height="50" rx="9" fill="var(--sl-color-bg)" stroke="var(--sl-color-hairline)" stroke-width="1.2" />
      <text x="147" y="352" class="sat" text-anchor="middle">Local terminal</text>
      <text x="147" y="369" class="satsub" text-anchor="middle">Claude Code</text>
    </g>
    <g>
      <rect x="488" y="330" width="170" height="50" rx="9" fill="var(--sl-color-bg)" stroke="var(--sl-color-hairline)" stroke-width="1.2" />
      <text x="573" y="352" class="sat" text-anchor="middle">Remote workhorses</text>
      <text x="573" y="369" class="satsub" text-anchor="middle">Perlmutter · Vast</text>
    </g>
  </svg>
  <figcaption>Not an agent runtime — the shared state every Claude session reads and writes.</figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .sub { margin: 2rem 0 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
  .sub svg { width: 100%; max-width: 640px; height: auto; }
  .sub .ctitle { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; fill: var(--sl-color-text); font-family: var(--sl-font-system, ui-sans-serif, sans-serif); }
  .sub .csub { font-size: 12px; fill: var(--sl-color-gray-3); font-family: var(--sl-font-system, ui-sans-serif, monospace); }
  .sub .sat { font-size: 12.5px; fill: var(--sl-color-text); font-family: var(--sl-font-system, ui-sans-serif, sans-serif); }
  .sub .satsub { font-size: 11px; fill: var(--sl-color-gray-3); font-family: var(--sl-font-system, ui-sans-serif, sans-serif); }
  .sub figcaption {
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
    font-style: italic;
    font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
</style>
